revisions.description: 1. Add Smart Cabinet related MIB nodes.
1. Add new trap named espNetworkUp for ES PDU.

1. Modify description of MIB node pduInputPhaseStatusCurrentState, pduInputPhaseStatusCurrent, pduInputPhaseStatusVoltage, pduInputPhaseStatusActivePower, pduInputPhaseStatusApparentPower and pduInputPhaseStatusPowerFactor.
1. Change node pduExternalSensorStatusAisle to be writable.
1. Add MIB node for daisy chain state.
1. Add one more attribute for all trap oids indicating pdu idx in case of daisy chain. 2. Add one more MIB node in order to reset network management card
1. Add MIB node for external sensor unique identifier. 2. Add MIB node for external sensor readings with higher Pricision.
1. change external sensor name doorContact to doorSwitch
1. change the enum value definition of external sensor threshold setting 2. Add a new node to enable/disable SSH connection 3. Add one more external sensor unit
1. Add one more node to enable/disable sensor
1. Changed descriptions for alarm thresholds. 2. Renamed pduOutletMeteredStatusEnergy to pduOutletMeteredStatusResettableEnergy. 3. Added pduUnitConfigOutletPeakPowerReset

1. Changed SYNTAX of pduUnitConfigUpperWarningThreshold SEQUENCE to Unsigned32 2. Changed SYNTAX of pduOutletSwitchedStateOnStartup to Integer32 3. Changed SYNTAX of pduServerPingEnabled to TruthValue 4. Added trapsInformationIndex to SEQUENCE of TrapsInformationEntry
